&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;UBC&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;Learning Module:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In line with my commitment to workforce development, I worked with the UBC to create a learning module for the Supervisory Career Training (SCT) Program. The SCT program provides training and development of UBC members in supervisory positions. The educational content was designed to be engaging, interactive, and thought provoking.&lt;/p&gt;
